{"tid":989131,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"IT intern 一問 (CS Year 1)","createTime":"2019-01-20T15:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T11:01:37.000Z","uid":231447,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d899bca69e67e21815d21fd878669c8af3490a0","tid":989131,"uid":231447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:25:28.000Z","msg":"小弟依家喺英國讀緊 computer science year 1<br />\n對 internship 有兩大問題<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔知點揀公司/職位：我睇好多人都話做 intern 應該跟大公司，對 CV 有貢獻，但問題係大公司都有好多，例如 cathay, BEA, HKBN 咁，究竟應該點揀？<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔知應唔應該申請果啲 6個月 至 1年 嘅 internship。有無師兄可以分享下應該點決定？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(第一次出po,如有錯漏,請輕插 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</span>"},{"pid":"adbdedecbe78df604dfdf95753f085469127f98f","tid":989131,"uid":231447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"同埋除咗 jobsDB, recruit. net 之類嘅 platform<br />\n有無咩推介可以喺邊度搵  相關 opportunities <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f8caa2216af45789b964a548980ef74dbc355d","tid":989131,"uid":8785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"adbdedecbe78df604dfdf95753f085469127f98f","tid":989131,"uid":231447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"同埋除咗 jobsDB, recruit. net 之類嘅 platform<br />\n有無咩推介可以喺邊度搵  相關 opportunities <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"搵咩公司就唔清楚<br />\n但最好都係上官網睇同報 唔好靠其他網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323350a2da2c62c85ad942870b04a0ece554e050","tid":989131,"uid":86277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T00:25:36.000Z","msg":"個人覺得，除非你知道畢業之後想入某一行做(banking, aviation etc.)否則都係揾啲it為主嘅大公司，肯定佢係有project俾你做，唔係打雜fax換燈膽嘅<br />\n起碼有實際嘅經驗可以寫落cv<br />\n<br />\n想畢業做ibank嘅記住揾ibank intern，之後易入好多(做ibank嘅fd講)"},{"pid":"119b41a90d72a67e65670